review_text: Zero affect on odor. This device works by pushing a small volume of air over a UVC light. It has no odor elimination because there is nothing in the device that could do so. It should not be marketed for odor, it’s just not possible with what this unit is capable of. Not recommended.

I already have an ergonomic expensive office chair that is rated for 8+ hours a day. This really made a fantastic addition. It is expensive but it is well worth it. I plan to buy another for my car.
